ANALYSIS
This bill directs the department of health and human services to seek approval from Centers for
Medicare and Medicaid Services to cover family caregiver support services as an allowable service
under specified waiver programs. The bill also eliminates the child care scholarship cost share for
childreninkinshipcare.
